-- Wilmar, China Cooking-Oil Companies to Increase Retail Prices, CBN Reports
-- B y   B l o o m b e r g   N e w s
-- 2010-10-13T23:38:43Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2010-10-13/china-cooking-oil-companies-to-raise-retail-prices-business-news-reports.html
Cooking oil companies in China plan
to raise retail prices soon, the China Business News reported
today, citing an unidentified official from China Corn Oil Co.  Companies that may raise prices for cooking oil products
include China Corn Oil Co., Shandong Luhua Group Co. and Wilmar
International Ltd., the report said. Some companies may increase
prices by about 10 percent, the newspaper reported.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Bloomberg News at 
 jliu42@bloomberg.net  